{"tid":1077080,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人會睇返同男朋友以前傾偈嘅whatsapp history ？","createTime":"2019-03-25T10:40:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T16:32:48.000Z","uid":65563,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"074debf256f5a4312df337360f9a7ad09a283bfb","tid":1077080,"uid":65563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T10:40:44.000Z","msg":"今日我無啦啦睇返，好大感觸。<br />\n<br />\n我知佢唔喺會成日講甜言蜜語嘅人，但佢曾經因爲想我開心而成日同我講，我好多謝佢咁就我，<br />\n<br />\n但我寧願佢做返自己，因為喺平時生活上、相處上，<br />\n我一樣感覺到佢有幾錫我、愛我同關心我，<br />\n<br />\n唔喺下下用把口講幾愛幾愛，就等於一段愛情有幾好，有幾sweet，<br />\n<br />\n間中講一句半句，更加Sweet。<br />\n<br />\n希望而家同我繼續拍拖嘅你更開心，放心繼續做自己，而家嘅我亦覺得而家嘅相處模式喺最舒服最開心。<br />\n<br />\n我真喺好愛我男朋友，好想將來喺我身邊嘅都喺佢。"},{"pid":"41d779bc766629427e836420a89baa71459564fb","tid":1077080,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T11:23:46.000Z","msg":"你真係一個好女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c0b794f8e14250e7e7057fb6d3aefaba1a2be51","tid":1077080,"uid":225998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:32:48.000Z","msg":"我都會！"}]}